The Limpopo High Court sitting in Thohoyandou has
sentenced Mathivha Phathutshedzo (31) of Tshikundamalema village, to life
imprisonment for the murder of a 92-year-old
woman.He was sentenced to a further 8 years for house breaking
and robbery. The court heard how on 17 December 2015, Phatsutshedzo  went to the homestead of the 92-year-old gogo
